info.title: Schema of RedisCache events published to Azure Event Grid
info.description: Describes the schema of the RedisCache events published to Azure Event Grid. This corresponds to the Data property of an EventGridEvent.

timestamp.description: The time at which the event occurred.

status.description: The status of this event. Failed or  succeeded
